author: Cherri Mossburg, CNN
title: Coronavirus is the leading cause of death in Los Angeles County
description: Claiming an average of 44 lives each day, coronavirus has now become the leading cause of death in Los Angeles County, Health Director Barbara Ferrer said.
content:
